[
    {
        "Key": 1,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "再次望见天空的时候，黑夜已经降临。如水的夜色填满了空气的每一部分，微凉的庭院里一片寂静，像是遗世独立的一隅，又仿佛从幽寂画卷截取的一段。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 2,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "萤火虫一样的光团是虚幻的，围绕在肴的身边，渐渐飘上天空——这些都是舍塔利用“树”集齐的信仰。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 3,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "可随着辰星完成净化，“树”中的所有信仰都消散了，舍塔真正的后手甚至来不及动用就化为了乌有，化成了温暖庭院的无数光点，它们将悉数回归本我。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 4,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "肴夜天光",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_girl010_01",
        "zh_CN": "还挺好看的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 5,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "站在廊桥上，肴情不自禁按住胸口，忽然转过头，用无比晶莹的目光注视着我。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 6,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "是啊，挺好看的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 7,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我看着像是沐浴在光雨间的少女，真心实意夸赞。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 8,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不过你的身体，还能挺得住吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 9,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "肴的新战术套装是赶在最后的时间制作出来的，在此之前，她可没有进行适应性训练，刚才还在激烈的实战中火力全开。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 10,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "肴夜天光",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_girl010_02",
        "zh_CN": "分析员，你别说，你还真别说……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "肴顿时深吸一口气，一下子涨红了脸。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她给我无声的凝视，可我很清楚自己在这一刻该做什么。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "b-1",
        "Flag": "b-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "b-1-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "走过去，伸手环住她的腰",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "肴夜天光",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_girl010_03",
        "zh_CN": "果然，还得是分析员懂我……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 15,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "肴夜天光",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_girl010_04",
        "zh_CN": "差点就站不住了……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 16,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你啊，就别逞强了。后面的路我背你吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 17,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "肴夜天光",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_girl010_05",
        "zh_CN": "呼……那就交给分析员了，我先晕一会……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 18,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "肴说完就毫不客气地往我怀里一歪，脑袋也靠在了我的胸口。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 19,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "见此一幕，我不由自主看向始终跟在我身边的辰星。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 20,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "辰星。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 21,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星琼弦",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_girl014_01",
        "zh_CN": "不用在意我，分析员。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 22,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星琼弦",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_girl014_02",
        "zh_CN": "肴是“重伤员”，现在享有优待是应该的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 23,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "辰星脸上带着一本正经的严肃表情，可这答复却让我想说的话一下子卡在了喉中。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 24,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 25,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星琼弦",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_girl014_03",
        "zh_CN": "分析员，我说错什么了吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 26,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "大概是见到我此刻有些古怪的表情，辰星一下子有些忐忑起来，而我看着她心虚的模样，虽然内心有些不忍，但却还是不得向她求助。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 27,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我其实是想说啊……肴已经没啥力气了，我松手她就可能倒下，需要你扶她一把，把她扶我背上。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 28,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星琼弦",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_girl014_04",
        "zh_CN": "……？？？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 29,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "霎时间，辰星的脸蛋就变得比熟透的苹果还要红上几分，看上去像是随时要冒蒸汽的样子。可她还是强忍着快要爆炸的羞耻感，乖乖帮忙将肴扶上了我的背后。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 30,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "看着恨不得变成鸵鸟将脑袋完全埋进胸口的辰星，我有些想笑，可内心更有无限的情愫在生出。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 31,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不过嘛，有些事，你可以说不在意，没关系，我可不能不放在心上啊。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 32,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "下次，什么时候，什么地方，想要怎么背，你来定。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 33,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我认真看向辰星。她脸上红透的羞耻之意缓缓散去，可她抬起的，凝望的我眼眸里却含上越发娇羞的水汽。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 34,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "紧接着，她上前一步，用力抱住我的胳膊，认真地回应。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 35,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "辰星琼弦",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_girl014_05",
        "zh_CN": "这可是分析员说的，我记住了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 36,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我的每句话你都能记住吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 37,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "辰星琼弦",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_girl014_06",
        "zh_CN": "用心记住和用脑子记住是不一样的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 38,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "真是大胆啊，辰星。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 39,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "辰星琼弦",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_girl014_07",
        "zh_CN": "其实还有更大胆的……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 40,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "是吗，那我可要好好期待下了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 41,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我背着筋疲力尽，好似处于半梦半醒之间的肴，与辰星说完悄悄话后，继续向前走去，想要找到一块能够歇息的地方。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 42,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "辰星将我的胳膊抱得很紧，她的表情看上去是在带着某种遐思走神。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 43,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她像是在思考，像是在酝酿着勇气，像是准备做出某种决定。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 44,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "一段时间后，外围的战斗完全停歇，她们也找到了我。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 45,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "里芙&芬妮",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_girl002_01",
        "zh_CN": "亲爱的！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 46,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "众人",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_girl016_01",
        "zh_CN": "分析员！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 47,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "众人",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_girl012_01",
        "zh_CN": "分析员……！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 48,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "一道道纤细的倩影向我冲了过来，扑向我，不分先后，将我淹没在其中。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 49,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这就是……我为之努力的意义啊。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 50,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我仰躺在草地上，努力伸直手臂，想要将她们悉数相拥，也放任殚精竭虑的自己在这片柔软中，坠入睡梦。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 51,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "时间转眼即逝。“斩首计划”结束的第三天，我再次来到陶的办公室。有与上次作战相关的事情，她要与我讨论。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 52,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我与她的谈话，向来都是直抒胸臆。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 53,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "陶",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_npc003_01",
        "zh_CN": "我们解剖了舍塔制造的人形假体，确定那个怪物只是被她的一段意识操控着，而非她的本人。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 54,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "陶",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_npc003_02",
        "zh_CN": "另外，根据现场遗留各项实验痕迹的推论，基本可以确定，舍塔是意外发现了信仰的秘密。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 55,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "居然是意外吗，也对……如果不是意外，她大可做得更决绝一些。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 56,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "舍塔留守在北庭卫的力量，很坚决地抵挡着我们的攻击。这是很正常，也很不正常的事情。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 57,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她本人不在那里，就说明她做好了失败的准备。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 58,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "既然做好了失败的准备，又为何要投入那样的力量？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 59,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……原来如此。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 60,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "陶",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_npc003_03",
        "zh_CN": "看来你已经想到了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 61,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "是啊，舍塔会做出这副姿态，只能是为了向某些人证明价值。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 62,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她确实不会错过这样的力量。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 63,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "罗赞那个女人，在那场战斗开始的时候，又藏身在何方呢？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 64,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "陶",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_npc003_04",
        "zh_CN": "不过你也不用太过担心，因为意外诞生的信仰实验，没那么快可以成熟地运作，诞生出成果。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 65,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "陶",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_npc003_05",
        "zh_CN": "想要成熟利用这套技术，还需要时间。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 66,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这也代表，我们会有一段缓冲期？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 67,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "陶",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_npc003_06",
        "zh_CN": "不一定是很快会有。不过在缓冲期到来的时候，你会知道的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 68,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你是想说，在那之前，她还会做些什么吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 69,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "陶",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_npc003_07",
        "zh_CN": "我更想提醒你的是，在缓冲之后，她会变得更加强大。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 70,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
