    },
    {
        "Key": 71,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "…而且，我们还有你作为后盾，不是吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 72,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "陶",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_npc003_08",
        "zh_CN": "后盾……吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 73,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她沉默了许久，脸上似乎有一丝感情的波动，可等我再细细看去时，她依旧是那副古波不惊的模样，仿佛方才的动摇和情绪的波动都是我的错觉。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 74,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "陶",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_npc003_09",
        "zh_CN": "……你该走了，我还有很多事要处理。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 75,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我微笑着看了陶一眼，起身离开她的办公室。卡罗琳就等在办公室的门外。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 76,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卡罗琳",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_npc002_01",
        "zh_CN": "聊完啦？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 77,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "是啊，让你久等了，小情报官。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 78,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卡罗琳",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_npc002_02",
        "zh_CN": "还好吧，你和陶董也没聊多久啊？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 79,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我指的是这几天让你久等了，有不少事情处理，一直都没找你。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 80,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "卡罗琳闻言，忍不住给了我一个可爱的白眼。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 81,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卡罗琳",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_npc002_03",
        "zh_CN": "怎么，我的分析员，哄好了她们，终于记起把我冷落了啊。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 82,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我听说了一件事，作战那天，你也很着急想去前线。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 83,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卡罗琳",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_npc002_04",
        "zh_CN": "唔唔，这你都知道了呀。不过看到你安全回来后，我就放心了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 84,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "如果有机会的话，新的义体，你有没有想法。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 85,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卡罗琳",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_npc002_05",
        "zh_CN": "喂，分析员，我只是没去前线，可我一直没有停下过为你工作，别想着压榨我啦。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 86,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "听到这句话，我便明白，她还没有放下内心的一些芥蒂，对于战场的芥蒂。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 87,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卡罗琳",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_npc002_06",
        "zh_CN": "您还是多为自己操心吧，让我看看你接下来的行程，等等，这是什么？你空出这几个小时要去做什么？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 88,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "小情报官，打听上司的隐私，可不在你的工作范围。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 89,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卡罗琳",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_npc002_07",
        "zh_CN": "隐~私~啊~啧啧。行，不打听就不打听呗。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 90,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卡罗琳",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_npc002_08",
        "zh_CN": "不过……晚上记得回来。有人在等你。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 91,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "怎么，小情报官突然有事要约我？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 92,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卡罗琳",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_npc002_09",
        "zh_CN": "那也得能排上队啊，是有其他人希望我嘱咐你。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 93,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我会回来的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 94,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卡罗琳",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_npc002_10",
        "zh_CN": "嗯，我会帮你转告的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 95,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "暂时从繁忙的公务脱离出来，我忙里偷闲，来到了一家精巧的小店。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 96,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "客人A",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_npc076_01",
        "zh_CN": "不知道谁干的，把全城的烟花都包圆了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 97,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "客人B",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_npc042_01",
        "zh_CN": "真好啊，是在准备很浪漫的仪式吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 98,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "客人A",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_npc076_02",
        "zh_CN": "哎，可惜我的生日没有烟花庆祝喽。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 99,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "客人B",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_npc042_02",
        "zh_CN": "没事，如果你运气好的话，说不定能蹭到一场大烟花呢。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 100,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我走进店里的时候，恰有零星两个客人在谈话。她们提到的烟花让我生出些兴趣，不过既然被买光了的话，大概要过段时间才能准备了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 101,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这时店员注意到我的出现，向我走了过来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 102,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "店员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_npc068_01",
        "zh_CN": "是playername先生吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 103,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嗯。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 104,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "店员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_npc068_02",
        "zh_CN": "让您久等了……您前些天定做的东西，都已经做好了。",
