    },
    {
        "Key": 105,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "已经好了吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 106,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "店员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_npc068_03",
        "zh_CN": "是的。先生买这个，是用来定情的吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 107,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我毫不犹豫点头。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 108,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "店员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_npc068_04",
        "zh_CN": "那么，要在上面再刻些字吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 109,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "可以吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 110,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "店员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_npc068_05",
        "zh_CN": "当然，这样的定情信物才更有意义。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 111,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嗯。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 112,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "然而等店员将纸笔交到我手中时，我却一时有些“笔塞”了。不是想不到该写什么，而是想要写的实在太多。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 113,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "店员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_npc068_06",
        "zh_CN": "如果客人一时想不到该在上面刻些什么，就想想你心仪的女孩好了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 114,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我的脑中闪过的是前几天的经历。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 115,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "思绪顿时如泉涌出。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 116,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "傍晚的尽头，我揣着对我而言沉甸甸的信物，返回了公司。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 117,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "可我还没有去找我想找的人，她们就出现在了我的眼前。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 118,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "肴夜天光",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_girl010_06",
        "zh_CN": "真困呐~分析员，你可算回来了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 119,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "可算回来……下午卡罗琳说的在等我的人，难道就是……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 120,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "肴夜天光",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_girl010_07",
        "zh_CN": "就是我们。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 121,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "辰星琼弦",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_girl014_08",
        "zh_CN": "分析员，我和肴有个礼物想送给你。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 122,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "礼物？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 123,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "肴夜天光",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_girl010_08",
        "zh_CN": "跟我们来，你就知道了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 124,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "肴笑吟吟地看着我，然后和辰星一左一右拉着我的手，带我去了天台。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 125,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这么神秘兮兮的，今天这上面能看到什么特别的风景吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 126,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "是落日还是满月？我猜着两人的想法，而等我真正和她们来到天台，看到的却是和往常一般无二的夜色。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 127,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "好像……天上也没什么特别的？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 128,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "肴夜天光",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_girl010_09",
        "zh_CN": "天上没有的，人间有啊。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 129,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "辰星琼弦",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_girl014_09",
        "zh_CN": "按照朔州的习俗，去了邪门的地方必须用些喜庆的东西来冲冲晦气。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 130,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "辰星琼弦",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_girl014_10",
        "zh_CN": "虽然过去了几天，但我想时间应该还不算晚。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 131,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "肴夜天光",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_girl010_10",
        "zh_CN": "我可是将半年的奖金都投进去了，接下来，你可要用心欣赏。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 132,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "肴夜天光",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_girl010_11",
        "zh_CN": "喂喂喂，可以开始啦！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 133,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "肴话音甫一落下，便有一道道破空声自天台外响起。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 134,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "夜色下，一颗颗彩色的星点逆着夜空往上飞去。它们跃过我们的头顶，跃到云层的上方，猛地炸开。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 135,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我仰头看着那一团团彩色的光，又缓缓低下头，看向在我面前的两人。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 136,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "烟花像是在她们的身后炸开，映照着两人的身影。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 137,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这是人间最绝的景色。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 138,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "肴夜天光",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_girl010_12",
        "zh_CN": "分析员，怎么样？没让你失望吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 139,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "没有，我很惊喜。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 140,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "肴夜天光",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep8_girl010_13",
        "zh_CN": "可你的语气，听着不怎么惊喜啊。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 141,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "因为我得压着自己的情绪，认真和你们说接下来的话。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
